lead_paragraph: Newcomer Chase Kalisz outduelled Olympic champion Ryan Lochte in the men's 400 meters individual medley final at the U.S. Olympic swim trials on Sunday, clinching the first ticket to the Rio Games.

headline.main: Kalisz Claims First Rio Ticket as Lochte Fades
